            "text_size": "40,15",
            "txt_align": "start",
            "sub_heading": "",
            "heading": "",
            "text": "<h2>What to Expect</h2><p></p><p>Throughout the 30 different drape styles, we’ll take you on a fashion journey that touches every vibe:</p><ul><li>Traditional drapes from across India<br/><br/></li><li>Office-ready looks<br/><br/></li><li>Boho fusion styling<br/><br/></li><li>Streetwear-inspired experiments<br/><br/></li><li>Wedding guest glam<br/><br/></li><li>Saree as a skirt, dress, dupatta, and more<br/><br/></li><li>And yes — sarees with sneakers, hoodies, and corsets!</li></ul><p>Each day, we'll explore a new way to rethink the saree — whether it’s by draping, pairing it with unconventional pieces, or styling it for unexpected occasions.</p><p>By the 30th drape, this won't just be a fashion diary — it'll be a celebration of personal style, sustainability, and saree storytelling. And who knows? You might never look at your wardrobe the same way again.</p>",
